{"tid":867051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑死人！中國公車等2小時都不來　結果一查竟是山寨假車站","createTime":"2018-10-18T10:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T10:52:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3779918626a7b154f1d2fd88c51b97f10cf13c1","tid":867051,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n中國是山寨大國這件事情，在這世界上應該沒有人不知道，而中國人的山寨能力之強，絕對是「只有中國人才能超過中國人」！日前四川一名男子，在公車站等了2小時，途經的7輛公車卻全都不靠站，結果最後他才發現原來該公車站牌竟然是假的，讓男子暴怒將事情PO到網路上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/18/1596178-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F1596178-XXL.jpg&h=7dfb2eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>▲▼山寨公車站牌（上圖）與真的公車站。（圖／翻攝自微博）</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/18/1596179-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F1596179-XXL.jpg&h=e65e6284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川一名胡姓男子，日前在「萬象新天地」公車站等車，想不到2個小時過去後，只有7輛公車經過，且這7輛公車全都不靠站，無言的胡男只能沿著路走了約1公里，才終於發現一個有公車停靠的公車站，上車後他出示苦等2小時未果的公車站牌照片，並詢問司機「為什麼沒人停車」，結果司機一看照片秒說該站牌是假的！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/10/18/1596177-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F1596177-XXL.jpg&h=0f6fb19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>▲山寨公車站牌死去。（圖／翻攝自微博）</strong><br />\n<br />\n氣憤地胡男回家後將事情經過PO到網路上，意外引起廣大迴響，原來是在附近蓋房子的建商自己偷立站牌，謊騙「交通方便」藉此拉高銷售，雖然該公司稱是在詢問公車公司獲得同意後才立的，不過卻遭公車公司打臉，指出完全沒這回事，最後「無辜的假站牌」只能承受眾人怨氣，被人凶狠的砸毀。（編輯：黃朝郁）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=444054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D444054&d=48Q0sfUiPCFtPlwj4gyWov7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2b913113\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D444054&h=c7a1dcc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?newsid=444054</a>"},{"pid":"eea3f3349bfbed8c98ac09eaa3adf26596a78450","tid":867051,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"只有騙子和強盜是真的世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ebfe5bb49546847df1711b848b72f1b2e523e88","tid":867051,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"強國得騙子係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}